Interface Condition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Test_Step_Element
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Expect_False, Expect_True
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConditionImpl, Expect_FalseImpl, Expect_TrueImpl

    public interface Condition
extends Test_Step_Element
    A representation of the model object 'Condition'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Refactoring
    • True steps
    • Warning
    • False steps

    See Also:
    TTCTestPackage.getCondition()
